code: public void testFilterChecks() throws IOException {     DeprecationIssue issue = DeprecationIssueTests.createTestInstance().     int numChecksPassed = randomIntBetween(0, 5).     int numChecksFailed = 10 - numChecksPassed.     List<Supplier<DeprecationIssue>> checks = new ArrayList<>().     for (int i = 0. i < numChecksFailed. i++) {         checks.add(() -> issue).     }     for (int i = 0. i < numChecksPassed. i++) {         checks.add(() -> null).     }     List<DeprecationIssue> filteredIssues = DeprecationInfoAction.filterChecks(checks, Supplier::get).     assertThat(filteredIssues.size(), equalTo(numChecksFailed)). }
